[{"id":"/sicpjs/2.3.1","tag":"TITLE","body":"2.3.1  \n    \n      引号\n      字符串"},{"tag":"TEXT","id":"#p1","child":[{"body":"\n\t到目前为止，我们使用字符串来显示消息，\n\t使用函数","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"JAVASCRIPTINLINE","body":"display"},{"body":" 和\n\t","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"JAVASCRIPTINLINE","body":"error"},{"body":" （例如在 \n\t练习 ","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"REF","body":"1.22","href":"/sicpjs/1.2.6#ex-1.22"},{"body":"中）。\n        我们可以使用字符串形成复合数据，并具有诸如这样的列表\n\t\nlist(\"a\", \"b\", \"c\", \"d\")\nlist(23, 45, 17)\nlist(list(\"Jakob\", 27), list(\"Lova\", 9), list(\"Luisa\", 24))\n          \n        \n        为了将字符串与名称区分开来，我们将它们括在\n\t\n\t中。 例如，JavaScript 表达式\n\t","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"JAVASCRIPTINLINE","body":"z"},{"body":" 表示\n\t名称 ","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"JAVASCRIPTINLINE","body":"z"},{"body":"的值，而 JavaScript\n\t表达式 ","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"JAVASCRIPTINLINE","body":"\"z\""},{"body":" 表示一个由单个字符组成的字符串，即英文字母表中最后一个字母的小写形式。\n      ","tag":"#text"}]},{"tag":"TEXT","id":"#p2","child":[{"body":"\n        通过引号，我们可以区分字符串和名称：\n        \n          ab\nconst a = 1;\nconst b = 2;\n          list_ab\nlist(a, b);\n          list_quote_a_quote_b\nlist(\"a\", \"b\");\n\t  list_quote_a_b\nlist(\"a\", b);\n          ","tag":"#text"}]},{"tag":"TEXT","id":"#p3","child":[{"body":" \n\t在节  ","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"REF","body":"1.1.6","href":"/sicpjs/1.1.6"},{"body":" ，我们介绍了\n\t ","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"JAVASCRIPTINLINE","body":" === "},{"body":" 和\n\t ","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"JAVASCRIPTINLINE","body":" !== "},{"body":" \n\t作为数字上的原语谓词。\n \n\t从现在开始，\n\t我们将允许两个字符串作为操作数\n","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"JAVASCRIPTINLINE","body":" === "},{"body":" 和\n\t ","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"JAVASCRIPTINLINE","body":" !== "},{"body":" 。谓词\n\t ","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"JAVASCRIPTINLINE","body":" === "},{"body":" \n\t当且仅当两个字符串相同时返回 true，并且\n","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"JAVASCRIPTINLINE","body":" !== "},{"body":" \n\t当且仅当两个字符串不同时返回 true。\n","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"FOOTNOTE_REF","id":"#footnote-link-1","body":"1","href":"/sicpjs/2.3.1#footnote-1"},{"body":" \n\t使用  ","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"JAVASCRIPTINLINE","body":" === "},{"body":" ，我们可以实现一个称为  ","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"JAVASCRIPTINLINE","body":" member "},{"body":" 。\n\t其接受两个参数：一个字符串和一个字符串列表或一个数字和一个数字列表。\n\t如果第一个参数不在列表中（即，不是\n","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"JAVASCRIPTINLINE","body":" === "},{"body":" 列表中的任何项），\n        则 \n ","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"JAVASCRIPTINLINE","body":"member"},{"body":" 返回\n\t","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"JAVASCRIPTINLINE","body":"null"},{"body":"。 否则，它返回\n\t列表中以该字符串或数字第一次出现的子列表开始：\n","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"SNIPPET","latex":false,"id":1,"eval":true,"prependLength":0,"program":"chap=2&prgrm=PTAEGUEkGEAVQFLlAJgHQGY0EYBQuAzAVwDsBjAFwEsB7E0AWwFMGAjJgJwAoqKWAaUAA8AlKADeuUNNAcmFIh3pUAzgH0SRADZauoqTMMyA-KE06DRwwC5QvFqAC8z0AAsmAQwAmekZavSpkL+AbbMbJw8fAyCFB5UuqIiANy4AL744ezcAEQeAA75Wkw5glqqFFw5+Z4cpaA5rB4kzR711RykJSIiQA","body":"function member(item, x) {\n    return is_null(x)\n           ? null\n           : item === head(x)\n           ? x\n           : member(item, tail(x));\n} "},{"body":" \n        例如，\n","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"SNIPPET","latex":false,"id":2,"eval":true,"prependLength":9,"program":"chap=2&prgrm=PTAEGUEkGEAVQFLlAJgHQGY0EYBQuAzAVwDsBjAFwEsB7E0AWwFMGAjJgJwAoqKWAaUAA8AlKADeuUNNAcmFIh3pUAzgH0SRADZauoqTMMyA-KE06DRwwC5QvFqAC8z0AAsmAQwAmekZavSpkL+AbbMbJw8fAyCFB5UuqIiANy4AL744ezcAEQeAA75Wkw5glqqFFw5+Z4cpaA5rB4kzR711RykJSIiQA","body":"member(\"apple\", list(\"pear\", \"banana\", \"prune\")) "},{"body":" \n        是","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"JAVASCRIPTINLINE","body":"null"},{"body":"，而\n         ","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"SNIPPET","latex":false,"id":3,"eval":true,"prependLength":9,"program":"chap=2&prgrm=PTAEGUEkGEAVQFLlAJgHQGY0EYBQuAzAVwDsBjAFwEsB7E0AWwFMGAjJgJwAoqKWAaUAA8AlKADeuUNNAcmFIh3pUAzgH0SRADZauoqTMMyA-KE06DRwwC5QvFqAC8z0AAsmAQwAmekZavSpkL+AbbMbJw8fAyCFB5UuqIiANy4AL744ezcAEQeAA75Wkw5glqqFFw5QqWgOQCetXmFxU35nhw5IiJAA","body":"member(\"apple\", list(\"x\", \"y\", \"apple\", \"pear\")) "},{"body":" \n        是","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"JAVASCRI